WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
The quickest way to search the Werkstatt 

00:03.000 --> 00:07.000
is with the simple search in the upper right-hand corner.

00:07.500 --> 00:14.000
You can search formulae collections, charter corpora or E-Lexicon articles.

00:14.500 --> 00:19.000
There is also a lemma search and an advanced search.

00:19.200 --> 00:22.000
These will be covered in their own videos.

00:22.500 --> 00:26.000
To search for a term, go to the simple search field,

00:26.500 --> 00:31.000
and type in the phrase for which you want to search,

00:32.000 --> 00:36.000
suggestions for phrases to search are shown

00:36.500 --> 00:39.000
(you need not choose any of these),

00:39.200 --> 00:41.000
then click on the box(es)

00:41.200 --> 00:43.000
for the corpora you wish to search,

00:43.200 --> 00:47.000
Formulae and Charters in this case,

00:47.200 --> 00:50.000
and then hit "Enter".

00:50.200 --> 00:54.000
The Werkstatt will be searched and the results shown here.

00:55.000 --> 01:03.000
You can filter, sort and download these search results.

01:03.200 --> 01:06.000
These functions will be explained in their own videos.

